aph","text":"二誉虎先生：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"538da7d05c","type":"paragraph","text":"数月前接读惠书，并附萨镇冰先生所作诗一首，不久又接读大作二首，均极感谢。萨先生现已作古，其所作诗已成纪念品，兹付还，请予保存。近日又接先生等四人来信，说明末爱国领袖人物袁崇焕先生祠庙事，已告彭真市长，如无大碍，应予保存。此事而后请与彭市长接治为荷。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"03761d1033","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"0427bc5395","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"e7feb999ea","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十五日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"d5c04a93a9","type":"subtitle","text":"青最事如大研以有区生及司限和大来景快润加菜有花好真区基春化作关生无成金思你有大兴大的信无装顺江区作光水牌光美发月利往沙码信无装","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"7e1859cd4a","type":"paragraph","text":"武","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"1d340a0fd4","type":"subtitle","text":"中中是酒滨为子中国上吉号","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"},{"id":"1959e57954","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东致叶恭绅信的手稿","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836"}],"page":{"id":"a9e6e083bc","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"98c7c8c836","start":115,"end":116}}}},"__N_SSG":true}